    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304670/extras/6b74790b478a36840c420732c7f23abb.avif?t=1763341904\" width=550 height=219 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>About This Demo</strong></h2>Play as Hendra, a man on a mission for revenge. Infiltrating a hidden, illegal factory, you'll come face-to-face with Jagal, one of those responsible for your family’s murder. Engage in close-quarters combat and uncover dark secrets as you take the first steps on your path to vengeance.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Story Mission</strong></h2> Experience a compelling, demo-exclusive mission where Hendra infiltrates a dangerous illegal factory to confront Jagal, the man responsible for your family's murder. Navigate intense close-quarters combat, face deadly enemies, and uncover the dark secrets within this criminal operation.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304670/extras/fdeef9a38c29cebce0ce46e40eb707a8.poster.avif?t=1763341904\" width=602 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304670/extras/fdeef9a38c29cebce0ce46e40eb707a8.webm?t=1763341904\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304670/extras/fdeef9a38c29cebce0ce46e40eb707a8.mp4?t=1763341904\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Arena Mode</strong></h2>  Test your skills in arena mode, where you’ll face relentless waves of enemies. This fast-paced combat experience challenges you to hone your tactics and strive for high scores unique to the demo.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304670/extras/59c2c600aa2053a753d67ff30a5288c6.poster.avif?t=1763341904\" width=602 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304670/extras/59c2c600aa2053a753d67ff30a5288c6.webm?t=1763341904\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304670/extras/59c2c600aa2053a753d67ff30a5288c6.mp4?t=1763341904\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Limited Outfit Selection</strong></h2> Personalize Hendra’s appearance with a selection of demo-only outfits. Each option allows you to style Hendra to match your gameplay approach, giving a glimpse of the customization available in the full game.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304670/extras/3e68eb5e1c502d2c7a84ec79c64973f8.poster.avif?t=1763341904\" width=602 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304670/extras/3e68eb5e1c502d2c7a84ec79c64973f8.webm?t=1763341904\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304670/extras/3e68eb5e1c502d2c7a84ec79c64973f8.mp4?t=1763341904\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Achievements</strong></h2> Unlock up to 10 demo-specific achievements tied to the story mission, arena scores, and combat challenges, encouraging you to fully explore and master the demo experience.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Key Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Demo-exclusive story mission with unique objectives and enemies<br></li><li>Arena mode featuring wave-based combat and high score challenges<br></li><li>Limited outfit customization to personalize Hendra’s look<br></li><li>Unlockable achievements tied to the story mission, arena scores, and combat challenges</li></ul>",
